publicwhip.minor-heading: Driver and Vehicle Licensing Agency: Databases

ques.p: To ask the Minister of State, Department for Transport how much was received in payments from private companies for information from the Driver and Vehicle Licensing Agency database in each of the last five financial years; and how much he estimates will be received from such payments in (a) 2009-10 and (b) 2010-11.
